frames.caption: A group of hooded figures ascends a steep, rocky path towards a towering, ominous fortress. The scene is shrouded in dark, smoky clouds, with the ground appearing to be stained with red hues, adding to the foreboding atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a dystopian or fantasy setting where cloaked individuals are making their way up a rugged incline towards a massive, dark fortress. The environment is bleak and threatening, with a sky filled with swirling clouds and a landscape that suggests desolation.

frames.caption: A group of armored figures approaches a dark, foreboding fortress under a stormy sky. The scene is filled with swirling debris and an ominous red glow emanating from the fortress. The atmosphere is tense and dramatic, suggesting an impending battle or confrontation.
frames.description: The scene depicts a medieval fantasy setting with a group of armored warriors advancing towards a massive, dark fortress. The environment is chaotic, with storm clouds and debris filling the air, creating a sense of urgency and danger.
